Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:41.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. Such a huge article...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:43.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As tall and as loud as they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the outfits they're sporting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after they returned, it's been pretty crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:49.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The "talks" really went all the way from there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:55.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, gather around! We need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Design is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:03.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll officially announce the splitting\Nfor the Tottori and Tokyo teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive how selfish we're being, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:13.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tottori, huh? That brings back memories...
