Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:19.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I bet the current A Team and B Team will\Nsplit up between Tokyo and Tottori, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:24.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'd like to let Tanaka-san, the newlywed, stay in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:26.42,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(350,0)\bord1.5\fscy80\fs37\shad0\3c&HDEE4FF&\c&H383BBE&\pos(549,233)}Tanaka-san\N{\i1\fs55\fnArial Black\fscx60}(B-Team)\N{\i0\fs37\fnVectora LT Roman\fscx90}\h\h\hHeading to Tottori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave my family behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.88,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz26\fnArial\shad0\bord4\be1\fscx55\fsp4\fs65\c&HAEAFF1&\move(841,-42,-66,378)\3c&HF3FDFC&}Newlywed
