Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:31.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, one member from Tokyo team\Nwill automatically get sent to Tottori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:35.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx60\fsp5\fs36\shad0\c&H399CDE&\3c&HEFF8FF&\pos(677,384)}Um... Miwako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who should we send?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx60\fsp5\fs36\shad0\c&H399CDE&\3c&HEFF8FF&\pos(329,474)}I'm a little cold, will you please hold me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, where did you go last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the storage, so if you have anything\Nyou want to put away, please take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you punk! What are you ignoring me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't fall for your provocations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:53.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, he's learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no fun. Have you grown up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:03:01.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we already know everything due to Asai-san's fax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:06.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy to escape from our twisted maze of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like Asai-san will be out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:14.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If Asai-san ends up retiring like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san will probably quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have my ambition of someday working with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:28.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like her to continue, no matter how.
