Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But for that, she'll need a replacement for Asai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a risky bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:37.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H283055&\shad0\bord0.5\be1\fs27\frz1.909\3c&H6567BF&\pos(431,233)}Mayama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:54.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, when everyone is finishing up their preparations\Nfor the Hamabi Festival, the flu goes around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. How's Takemoto doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to have a cold, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:07.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto isn't the only one acting funny at this time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The graduate thesis and the job hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A time like that comes for every senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And please eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That we finished all the jobs that had\Nbeen asked of Harada Design?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:11.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Rika-kun say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still jobs left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she knew that you would get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:26.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her that maybe she should ask you\Nto come back, but she won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That she hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt really at ease when I was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he doesn't know about Harada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know about my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:44.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when I was with him, I didn't\Nhave to pretend that I'd gotten over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I could concentrate on my work without\Nworrying about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:54.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the while, that boy just quietly stood by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:06:00.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that I was {\i1}truly{\i0} being saved by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:05.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that accident, she's been blaming herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If she feels any amount of fun or joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:14.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,she's immediately overcome with guilt and\Npushes those things away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun, you might just be one of\Nthose things that she pushed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:30.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what blaming yourself and pushing\Neverything away, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will lead you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say anything to her, I only wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I struggled tremendously and desperately...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:54.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... I only learned something small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain which tears my heart apart just thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:03.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That this pain is enough reason for me\Nnot to distance myself from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:12.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of information has leaked out already, but as of\Nthis December, Fujiwara Design will split into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:15.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The teams will be split according to the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.37,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\c&H283055&\be1\shad0\bord0.1\fs28\3c&H4C4C4C&\pos(101,361)}Nakano
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.37,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,200)\c&H283055&\be1\shad0\bord0.1\fs28\3c&H4C4C4C&\pos(437,103)}Mayama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mario-san, please hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama isn't staying in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's selfish of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:24.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I promise you that he'll be treated well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please follow our decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it at a time like this, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx60\fsp5\fs32\shad0\c&H399CDE&\3c&HEFF8FF&\pos(598,461)}Have all the complicated talks ended?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx60\fsp5\fs32\shad0\c&H399CDE&\3c&HEFF8FF&\pos(182,345)}How about a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,President, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:44.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Just run like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's quitting so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's certainly a green spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll get a little lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, isn't it said that you should make your precious child travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:10.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nomiya, Miwako-san! How can\Nboth of you be so calm about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that I'm being left out of the group?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:22.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Asai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I bring out the desk that I was using before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just treat me as a temporary employee at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pushing myself onto you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:46.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you think that I'm useful, please employ me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:47.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fujiwara Design?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just how things went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I borrow these two monitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... that means, Mayama-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some while it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Mayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you when I left this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'll come back, even if you're not waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said this at the hospital, but I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please employ me at Harada Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be more useful than I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end up hurting you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, you can hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I won't be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon calls for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In a sweet and endless melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:58.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I gently cover her ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came back to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.18,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord0.1\be1\shad0\fsp3\fs60\fscx126\move(542,-19,542,-205)\3c&HE7E8EB&\frz266\c&H818083&}Wedding Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so glad it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How merry, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Having the ceremony in your hometown is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:31.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your neighborhood, so everyone can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:35.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, look at how nervous Tat-chan looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And compared to him, just look at how composed the bride is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi-chan sure is looking beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:47.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure has been a while since a youngster from\Nthe Hamadayama Shopping District got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord2\fscx60\fsp7\fs35\be1\c&H797FDA&\move(473,455,408,455)\3c&HEDF1FF&}"Grandma, it's a bride!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Golly, congratulations, Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a joyous occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:58.47,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\shad0\bord0.2\be1\fsp1\fs34\pos(439,41)\c&H848F98&\3c&H85909A&}One rival has dropped out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, it's celebration sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:02.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, this is so festive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look beautiful, Akemi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We made the right choice to go with white.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:12.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Aunt Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is a wonderful outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:18.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if it's okay for me to be wearing\Nwhite when this is my second wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no second or fifth time for a joyous occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to keep working at the bar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should make a lot of requests from your husband now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:32.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, when you do, order from my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:36.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Of course... Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:41.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The bride's eyes just shined suspiciously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:46.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the fearsome Misuzu sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:52.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Their family has held a firm grip on the wallets, hearts and secrets\Nof the men of the Hamadayama Shopping District for 52 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:55.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They intend on squeezing even more money out of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.41,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\fs64\fnTimes New Roman\bord0.5\fsp3\b0\be1\shad0\c&HE88DDE&\3c&H574C56&\pos(432,381)\fscx62.5\fscy65}Misuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,50)\fs28\3c&H29173F&\fnArtificeSSK\bord0.5\be1\b0\shad0\fscx60\fscy91.25\c&H9551E5&\pos(285,181)}Oldest Sister\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\c&HBC7AEE&}Akemi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.53,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,50)\fs28\3c&H29173F&\fnArtificeSSK\bord0.5\be1\b0\shad0\fscx60\fscy91.25\pos(701,227)\c&H6327D5&}Second Sister\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMachiko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.45,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,50)\fs28\3c&H29173F&\fnArtificeSSK\bord0.5\be1\b0\shad0\fscx60\fscy91.25\pos(316,426)\c&H894ADC&}Third Sister\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\c&H7022E1&}Chouko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.99,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,150)\fs37\3c&H29173F&\fnArtificeSSK\bord0.9\be1\b0\shad0\fscx50\fsp5\fscy91.25\pos(636,328)\c&H6B33E9&}Second Generation Hostess\NMizue
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:06.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that we got the first groom out of\Nthe Third Generation Association, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Tatsukichi from the sushi restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:14.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably going to start conning us into ordering\Nexpensive sushi now for the rest of our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:16.13,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,500)\fnFluid-Light\fscy85\bord0.5\be1\shad0\fs25\pos(618,78)\c&H537282&\3c&H537282&}Sushikichi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Tatsukichi-san? A party of six, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Tatsu-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some celebration sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:36.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, but a little... l-l-lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsu-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:44.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here, Ayu, Tatsu-san is mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't touch him so easily anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Ayu, how many drinks have you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is the biggest problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also problematic that she doesn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't cry, Tatsukichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:10.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all your fault, Ayu, if the Hamadayama Shopping\NDistrict goes extinct after the third generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I've always cared about Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ayu is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:07.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, she's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:08.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I won't let you have Ayu, she's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:16.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, don't be depressed about failed love for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch your mindset and start looking\Nfor a new man and a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be causing problems for your parents for long either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, Akemi-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:32.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this day and age, there aren't\Nthat many good men or good jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you really run out of a place to go, come to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can start Misuzu Store No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The bride's eyes just shined suspiciously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.14,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\fad(300,0)\shad0\bord0\pos(538,461)\fscx80\c&HFFFFFC&}The night before the Hamabi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:48.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He made a tall object, that's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:57.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this was done on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks as if it's about to collapse, but it's not collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takemoto-kun's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:08.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He has great techniques, but he's a little\Nlacking in the creativity department...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:14.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a serious, hard-working student...\Nbut how should we judge this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, professors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many displays this year, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hanamoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Takemoto-kun's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Isn't it a masterpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.90,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}The Tower of Adolescence — Takemoto Yuuta
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is random yet refined...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:42.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The lack of planning, yet the stoicism that I sense in it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:45.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:49.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really makes me reminisce about those\Ndays when I was so confused as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:53.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days when I kept struggling and striving,\Neven though I didn't even know who I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:57.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening? I can't stop the tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I give this an 80!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a 90!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't hold back anymore.
