Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You finished the one from the other day already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been coming around a lot lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, what should I get tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:29.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to deposit your pay, so can you give me\Nyour account number and cell phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, for things like that, if you could\Njust go through Mayama like usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:40.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't heard yet that Mayama quit, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:42.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.90,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\fad(250,0)\be1\bord1\shad1\fscx80\c&HFCFFFF&\pos(593,460)\3c&H292E2D&\4c&H292E2D&}The Day of Hamabi Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to Yamada-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's burned out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:06.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear she passed out at her store last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What in the world happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave her be for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
