Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The objet moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.10,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}objet {\be1\3c&H000000&}= curio; a novel, possibly bizarre art object
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's started already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pocket warmers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:51.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:54.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu! I need to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:01.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:13.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? You were proposed to by four guys at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you ran away from them, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:47.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the four are all older guys from the shopping district\Nthat you've been friends with from long ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone among them that you think is kind of nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:58.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean... we've always been together since we\Nwere little, and t-they've always been so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just never thought of them like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:07.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've always been friends and things were going great...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they need to say something like that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:16.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they didn't tell me that they liked me,\Nwe could've been friends forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:22.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:28.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san already knew how everyone felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.30,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:36.31,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you get angry\Nat me, I probably won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.81,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to fall in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:44.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:46.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:55.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you heard about Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:03.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd always thought that Mayama was an idiot and a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:09.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered, why can't he like me when\NI've liked him so much for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:10.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then in my case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:19.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If the guys from the shopping district pressed me, "Why\Naren't we good enough, when we like you so much?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:25.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If they said, "We've liked you for so long,\Nyou need to choose one of us."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if they said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:32.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really precious to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't ever do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:44.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how Mayama must have felt... that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:49.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a lot quicker if you just found another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I say to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:20:00.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need to tell everyone now, what I hated to have myself told?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only keep trying or give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:11.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the only two choices we humans ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is to tell them your honest feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:17.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep trying, or to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:23.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'll be their turn to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lied about one thing to Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:02.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are actually three choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:08.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But a path will open up easier when you\Nbelieve that there are only two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:15.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't mention the third choice.
